Package org.eclipse.persistence.jpa.jpql.parser

Class AbstractEclipseLinkTraverseParentVisitor

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.eclipse.persistence.jpa.jpql.parser.AnonymousExpressionVisitor
      • org.eclipse.persistence.jpa.jpql.parser.AbstractTraverseParentVisitor
        • org.eclipse.persistence.jpa.jpql.parser.AbstractEclipseLinkTraverseParentVisitor
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    EclipseLinkExpressionVisitor, ExpressionVisitor
    public abstract class AbstractEclipseLinkTraverseParentVisitor
extends AbstractTraverseParentVisitor
implements EclipseLinkExpressionVisitor
    This EclipseLinkExpressionVisitor traverses up the hierarchy. It is up to the subclass to complete the behavior.

    Provisional API: This interface is part of an interim API that is still under development and expected to change significantly before reaching stability. It is available at this early stage to solicit feedback from pioneering adopters on the understanding that any code that uses this API will almost certainly be broken (repeatedly) as the API evolves.

    Version:
    2.5
    Author:
    Pascal Filion
    Since:
    2.4
